  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You use your chakra to create a sealing formation stretching from yourself to a target creature you can see within range, in a straight line. Target creatures must make a Charisma saving throw, reducing both your movement speed and the targets to 0 on a failed save. This can be used with others targeting the same creature, increasing the Save DC by +1 for each additional user. At the end of the target creatures turn, they remake their save.</p>",
